Class AbstractVector<E,V extends AbstractVector<E,V,N,P>,N,P>

  • Object
    • AbstractVector<E,V,N,P>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements of the vector
    V - The type of the vector
    N - The type of the taxicab and max norm of the vector
    P - The type of the inner product
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BigDecimalVector, BigIntegerVector, RealComplexNumberVector, SimpleComplexNumberVector
